1
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:34,970
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:38,009
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,660
How could this happen?

4
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:45,000
He went straight to bed after he came back

5
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,729
and has been asleep ever since.

6
00:01:47,009 --> 00:01:48,470
He hasn't eaten anything.

7
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:52,130
Is it still because of the Yan people
entering the city?

8
00:01:52,430 --> 00:01:53,960
News from the frontier says

9
00:01:54,759 --> 00:01:57,120
that since Zhaluowahan,
the Emperor of Yan,

10
00:01:57,120 --> 00:02:00,150
agreed to send an envoy delegation
for Dan's birthday celebration,

11
00:02:00,150 --> 00:02:01,510
it has been half a month.

12
00:02:01,710 --> 00:02:04,040
They still haven't reached an agreement.

13
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,630
I can't enter the court,

14
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,400
so I don't know the details.

15
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,830
Is it the Empress Dowager who opposes it,

16
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,430
or Prince Duan?

17
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,530
Both of them.

18
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:18,390
It was expected that the Empress Dowager
would oppose it.

19
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:21,360
After all, if the peace talks succeed
and there's no war,

20
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:24,160
Prince Duan's troops
won't be tied up at the border

21
00:02:24,190 --> 00:02:26,320
and could instead be used against her.

22
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,090
But we didn't expect

23
00:02:28,710 --> 00:02:32,470
that Prince Duan, perhaps fearing
that the army would be hard to control

24
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,840
if it returned to the capital,
would also be against it.

25
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:37,100
We still haven't figured out a solution.

26
00:02:38,140 --> 00:02:40,600
These people
claim to care about the nation,

27
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:43,710
but who cares about Dan's life and safety?

28
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:46,310
His health is fragile already,

29
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:48,040
and he suffers from headaches.

30
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:56,520
Indeed.

31
00:02:57,480 --> 00:03:00,140
These ministers
treat him like a fool every day,

32
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:04,400
and he has to deal with each of them
while pretending to be one.

33
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,000
I can hide in the Cold Palace,

34
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,710
but where can he hide?

35
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:11,590
This is the secret letter
Dan brought back.

36
00:03:12,730 --> 00:03:13,390
Take a look.

37
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:16,550
It was after reading this letter

38
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,610
that his headache flared up again.

39
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:22,310
[Emperor of Yan is hospitable.
I couldn't refuse his hospitality]

40
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,329
Emperor of Yan is hospitable.
I couldn't refuse his hospitality...

41
00:03:22,329 --> 00:03:24,480
[I'm afraid I'll have to stay here for
a few days and will be late. Wang Zhao]

42
00:03:24,950 --> 00:03:27,410
Wang Zhao
was detained by the Emperor of Yan?

43
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,320
Mr. Bei,

44
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:35,530
I've been in the Cold Palace
for 2 months now.

45
00:03:35,530 --> 00:03:37,360
I don't need to pay respects
to the Empress Dowager,

46
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:40,020
and I've been cut off
from Prince Duan's spying.

47
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:42,640
It's like taking an extremely long leave.

48
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:48,650
But I can't keep hiding like a coward,

49
00:03:49,010 --> 00:03:51,010
leaving him alone to deal with them.

50
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,220
You want to leave the Cold Palace?

51
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,480
That's right.

52
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,470
But didn't Dan
tell you to wait a little longer

53
00:03:57,470 --> 00:04:00,000
until he finds a reason
for your restoration?

54
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,160
I have to think...

55
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,590
what reason I could use.

56
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:11,750
[Office of Drums and Bells]

57
00:04:11,870 --> 00:04:13,330
I'm innocent!

58
00:04:13,690 --> 00:04:16,100
[Office of Drums and Bells]

59
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:16,209
I suffer in this Cold Palace every day,

60
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,390
calling to heaven and earth for help

61
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,510
to no avail!

62
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,720
And the real culprit is out there,

63
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,510
living carefree!

64
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:26,760
Today,

65
00:04:26,970 --> 00:04:29,960
[Office of Drums and Bells]

66
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:29,720
I will expose her scheme to the world!

67
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:32,320
Everyone in the palace,

68
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:34,480
young and old, girls and maids,

69
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,830
please judge this!

70
00:04:38,870 --> 00:04:39,790
Your Majesty,

71
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:40,800
I specially prepared

72
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:43,200
this rose essence for you myself.

73
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,560
After using it,

74
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:47,450
your skin will be firm,
smooth, and elastic.

75
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:50,270
-Your Majesty!
-And the fragrance will last...

76
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,830
Your Majesty,

77
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:56,159
please help me get justice, Your Majesty!

78
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,390
What's going on?

79
00:04:57,630 --> 00:05:00,560
Why are you crying
so early in the morning?

80
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:02,450
Your Majesty, you have no idea,

81
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:03,460
but Concubine Yu

82
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,950
has gone mad!

83
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,310
She's been locked in the Cold Palace.

84
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:09,440
How could she still cause you trouble?

85
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,640
I thought

86
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,460
she would behave from then on,

87
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,530
but this morning she was shouting

88
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:15,820
and claiming

89
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,630
that I'm the real culprit

90
00:05:17,950 --> 00:05:19,830
and she's the victim.

91
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,320
Are you the real culprit?

92
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,000
I'm not.

93
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:25,560
So what are you afraid of?

94
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:27,360
If a mad dog bites you,

95
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,690
are you going to bite it back?

96
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,050
But the things she said were awful.

97
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:34,190
Now the whole harem is spreading

98
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,680
that she's innocent.

99
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:38,000
If His Majesty hears this...

100
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:39,510
Your Majesty!

101
00:05:39,630 --> 00:05:42,720
Please help me get justice, Your Majesty!

102
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,950
Alright, alright.

103
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:46,270
If the Emperor blames you,

104
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:49,120
I will certainly stand up for you.

105
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:49,830
Let's go.

106
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,210
Consort Shu.

107
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,320
The floor is cold. Get up.

108
00:06:01,390 --> 00:06:02,450
What's happening?

109
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,410
She vomited?

110
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:04,950
Consort Xie.

111
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,800
Hurry up and summon the imperial physician

112
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,950
to check on Consort Xie!

113
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:09,430
Yes.

114
00:06:18,310 --> 00:06:19,600
Come on.

115
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:21,720
My problem hasn't been resolved yet.

116
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,090
Sister Shu,

117
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:26,240
there's something
I've known for a long time.

118
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:28,190
I just don't know
whether I should tell you.

119
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,000
Yes.

120
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,690
I've recorded everything.

121
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,690
If I show it to you,

122
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,190
you mustn't get angry.

123
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:37,730
These are all the bad things
Yu Wanyin has said about you.

124
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,300
Yu Wanyin!

125
00:06:56,940 --> 00:07:00,400
[Office of Drums and Bells]

126
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:58,990
You two,

127
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:00,480
open the door!

128
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:01,240
Your Highness,

129
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,430
His Majesty ordered that no one may enter.

130
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:05,960
A lowly discarded concubine
wants to stop me?

131
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:06,830
Your Highness,

132
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,240
please don't make things difficult for us.

133
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:08,870
Stop it.

134
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,600
You know very well the relationship

135
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,600
between my brother and the Imperial Guard.

136
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,260
Step aside!

137
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,040
Oh my.

138
00:07:13,670 --> 00:07:15,670
Consort Shu is so efficient.

139
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,360
I'm not even ready yet.

140
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:18,140
Come here.

141
00:07:18,870 --> 00:07:20,680
Yu Wanyin, come out!

142
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:21,480
Your Highness.

143
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,920
Give this letter to Prince Duan

144
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,120
and notify Eunuch An.

145
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,000
-Yu Wanyin!
-Without my order,

146
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,040
you must not show yourselves.

147
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,050
-Yes, Your Highness.
-If you've got the nerve,

148
00:07:27,050 --> 00:07:28,180
-Go.
-open the door!

149
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,360
Yu Wanyin!

150
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,250
Yu Wan...

151
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,600
Sister Shu?

152
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,830
What brings you here?

153
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:36,190
How dare you ask me that?

154
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:38,070
Don't you know what you've done?

155
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,800
I don't know. Please tell me.

156
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,530
Two months ago you said I...

157
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:44,870
What did I say?

158
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:45,530
I...

159
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:47,240
I said

160
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:49,350
you're obsessed with novels

161
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:50,600
and have the complete

162
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,310
The Domineering Prince and Me series?

163
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,159
Shut up!

164
00:07:53,159 --> 00:07:54,890
Or did I say your taste is awful,

165
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:57,159
always wearing garish colors,

166
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,540
but in reality,

167
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,390
you can't tell red from green

168
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:01,520
or blue from yellow?

169
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:04,310
Or did I say that you hate bathing

170
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:06,120
and cover your smell with perfume,

171
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,980
which makes people want to vomit?

172
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:12,100
You...

173
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:12,680
I...

174
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,500
I'm not!

175
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
Yu Wanyin, you...

176
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:18,430
Come here right now!

177
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:18,890
Come...

178
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:19,680
out!

179
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,480
Yu Wanyin!

180
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,850
I was just telling the truth,

181
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,300
and you can't stand it?

182
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:30,910
Yu Wanyin!

183
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:34,200
I haven't even mentioned
all the details about how your family

184
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,200
framed my father.

185
00:08:36,539 --> 00:08:40,450
[Office of Drums and Bells]

186
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:37,360
Give it to me!

187
00:08:40,510 --> 00:08:41,840
-Yu Wanyin!
-Your Highness, please don't!

188
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,500
Your Highness! Please don't!

189
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,630
Yu Wanyin!

190
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:50,970
By this time next year
it will be your death anniversary!

191
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:53,520
She didn't grow
all that flesh for nothing.

192
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,960
-Yu Wanyin!
-Calm down!

193
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:01,120
Ganging up on me?

194
00:09:01,630 --> 00:09:03,630
You think I have no way to fight back?

195
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:04,650
What can you do?

196
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:06,840
I can run!

197
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,000
What are you waiting for? Chase her!

198
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:11,750
Let's go!

199
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:12,150
Hurry!

200
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,200
Stop right there!

201
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:23,440
Don't run!

202
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,680
Yu Wanyin!

203
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,040
Open the door!

204
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,070
Open the door!

205
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,120
Haven't you eaten?

206
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:43,340
Give me the axe!

207
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:44,700
Move aside!

208
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:47,960
His Majesty is here!

209
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,040
Take her away.

210
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:10,750
Confine her.

211
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:11,960
Your Majesty, let me explain!

212
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,020
It's not like that!

213
00:10:13,030 --> 00:10:13,560
Yu Wan...

214
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:15,960
Your Majesty!

215
00:10:15,960 --> 00:10:17,030
Your Majesty, I was wrong!

216
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:17,830
Your Majesty!

217
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:19,870
Your Majesty, please don't!

218
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,320
Your Majesty!

219
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:21,720
CEO Dan...

220
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,600
Your Majesty!

221
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,360
Boss Dan!

222
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,380
I led Consort Shu here.

223
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:26,560
It was just an act.

224
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,690
If you do this,

225
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:30,000
Prince Duan
will know I didn't fall out of favor.

226
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,120
Then all our previous performances

227
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,110
would have been for nothing.

228
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,670
If I don't punish her severely this time,

229
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:36,510
next time someone else
will be chasing you with an axe.

230
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:38,320
I'm not that unpopular.

231
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:40,610
I said I would find a proper reason

232
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:42,720
to bring you out of the Cold Palace.

233
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,420
Why did you act on your own?

234
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,240
I came in time this time.

235
00:10:46,870 --> 00:10:48,130
What if I'd been later?

236
00:10:48,530 --> 00:10:50,390
Weren't the secret guards there?

237
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,960
I was wrong.

238
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,750
Alright?

239
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,720
I know you want to protect me,

240
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,460
but I don't want your protection.

241
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,020
Because...

242
00:11:08,780 --> 00:11:10,240
I want to stand by your side

243
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,800
and fight together with you.

244
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:16,230
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

245
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:17,780
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

246
00:11:18,130 --> 00:11:20,310
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

247
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:22,090
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

248
00:11:22,130 --> 00:11:24,470
♪ Words unspoken ♪

249
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:28,480
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

250
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,360
So how should we act next?

251
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:32,300
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

252
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:32,450
Does this mean you forgive me?

253
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,640
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

254
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:36,120
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

255
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,080
I've thought it all through.

256
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:36,790
We'll say

257
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:37,950
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

258
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,670
that Consort Shu
caused a scene in the Cold Palace,

259
00:11:38,050 --> 00:11:40,550
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

260
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,720
and after an investigation,

261
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,150
you realized I was truly innocent.

262
00:11:42,050 --> 00:11:45,390
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

263
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:46,680
Then I immediately
restore your consort title

264
00:11:45,970 --> 00:11:49,400
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

265
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,050
and beg you desperately

266
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,030
to come back?

267
00:11:50,070 --> 00:11:53,060
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

268
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,120
But

269
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,240
I've already suffered so much,

270
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,510
grown distant from you,

271
00:11:53,500 --> 00:11:55,400
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

272
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,480
and my heart

273
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:57,310
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

274
00:11:57,030 --> 00:11:58,320
is open only to Prince Duan now.

275
00:11:57,570 --> 00:11:59,230
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

276
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:01,680
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

277
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:05,250
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

278
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,090
So

279
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:05,200
I lost your foresight

280
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,960
and could only grieve alone in sorrow.

281
00:12:06,130 --> 00:12:08,460
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

282
00:12:08,530 --> 00:12:09,680
♪ Still unchanged ♪

283
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,640
This is called

284
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,870
"karma for the late-blooming love"

285
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:13,000
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

286
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,050
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

287
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,080
Then, my beloved wife,

288
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:15,630
let's take

289
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:22,430
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

290
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,500
the secret passage for one last time.

291
00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:30,390
[Kunyu Palace]

292
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:45,890
Your Highness.

293
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:51,840
Consort Xie.

294
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:55,870
I've brought an imperial physician
to see you.

295
00:12:56,120 --> 00:12:58,120
Ms. Tonghao, how thoughtful of you.

296
00:12:58,200 --> 00:13:01,390
Perhaps it was something
I ate for breakfast.

297
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:04,270
Or maybe Consort Shu's powder

298
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:05,930
had too strong a scent.

299
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:07,550
But I'm fine now.

300
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,790
In that case,

301
00:13:09,270 --> 00:13:11,750
you need the imperial physician
to check on you more.

302
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:13,840
It will also put Her Majesty at ease.

303
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:25,910
Ling,

304
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:28,070
serve tea to Ms. Tonghao.

305
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,240
Yes.

306
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,510
No need.

307
00:13:31,390 --> 00:13:33,360
Once the imperial physician
has finished the examination,

308
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,890
I need to go back and report.

309
00:13:58,790 --> 00:13:59,720
I deserve death!

310
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:02,800
I was so clumsy.
Please forgive me, Your Highness!

311
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:13,310
Physician Xiao, what's the diagnosis?

312
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:24,300
Consort Xie
doesn't have a stomach problem,

313
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,210
nor is she sensitive to smells.

314
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:31,430
It's just that

315
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,800
she didn't sleep well.

316
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:43,730
Physician Xiao
said her pillow was too high,

317
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:46,480
which compressed the blood vessels
in her neck

318
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:49,080
and caused her dizziness and vomiting.

319
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:52,870
Physician Xiao?

320
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:57,450
Who is this Physician Xiao?

321
00:14:58,670 --> 00:14:59,960
Is he reliable?

322
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,430
Our familiar Physician Zhang

323
00:15:02,510 --> 00:15:04,270
happened to be out of the palace,

324
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:06,400
so I appointed a new junior physician.

325
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,030
His position is not yet secure,

326
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:09,720
so he couldn't have been bribed.

327
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:11,750
Therefore, he has no reason to lie.

328
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:16,440
Another false hope.

329
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:19,150
I thought

330
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:24,480
the Emperor
was giving me a little grandson.

331
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,540
He's still so useless.

332
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:33,510
Back then, His Majesty

333
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:36,640
was traumatized
by that assassin beauty from Yan State.

334
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,080
Perhaps

335
00:15:38,630 --> 00:15:40,330
since then,

336
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:41,630
it has been

337
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:44,420
difficult for him
to perform in the bedroom.

338
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:49,240
Otherwise, it wouldn't be so difficult
to have a little Crown Prince.

339
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:51,700
Difficult for him
to perform in the bedroom?

340
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:53,000
That's just an act.

341
00:15:55,150 --> 00:15:58,550
He knew he was just a puppet.

342
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:01,870
If he had disobeyed,

343
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:06,150
there would have been a younger,
more obedient prince replacing him,

344
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:08,720
and then he would have been useless.

345
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,150
You mean...

346
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:13,510
back then His Majesty was just pretending

347
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:15,040
he had no interest in women?

348
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,550
Whether he was pretending or not,

349
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:20,720
wasn't he still at my disposal?

350
00:16:21,630 --> 00:16:22,630
But Your Majesty,

351
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:25,260
you already had the little Crown Prince.

352
00:16:25,370 --> 00:16:26,030
Why

353
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,930
did you still want more?

354
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:32,280
You've been with me for so long,

355
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:34,630
yet you're still so brainless.

356
00:16:40,310 --> 00:16:43,510
If it weren't for Xiahou Bo
keeping a covetous eye on him,

357
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,550
how could Xiahou Dan

358
00:16:45,550 --> 00:16:47,670
have taken my words so seriously?

359
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:50,720
Remember,

360
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:53,860
never let your piece

361
00:16:53,910 --> 00:16:55,590
become the only

362
00:16:55,870 --> 00:16:57,840
irreplaceable one.

363
00:16:58,400 --> 00:17:00,730
Thank you for the guidance, Your Majesty.

364
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,620
That Physician Zhang—

365
00:17:03,870 --> 00:17:05,270
quickly call him back

366
00:17:06,829 --> 00:17:08,730
to examine Consort Xie properly.

367
00:17:09,589 --> 00:17:10,640
I don't trust

368
00:17:11,349 --> 00:17:13,430
strangers.

369
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,780
Yes, Your Majesty.

370
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,839
I will arrange it right away.

371
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:28,970
Consort Xie.

372
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:31,960
Physician Xiao.

373
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:35,530
Thank you for your help

374
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,500
earlier today.

375
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:38,480
Consort Xie,

376
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,460
the fetus has just formed,

377
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,920
and your pulse is not easy to detect.

378
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,880
I can only help you conceal it

379
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,590
temporarily.

380
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:02,200
So it's true.

381
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:06,510
Although I haven't been
in the Imperial Medical Bureau long,

382
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:08,470
I know a little about the risks

383
00:18:09,030 --> 00:18:10,760
of being pregnant in the harem.

384
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:13,790
I understand your situation,
Your Highness.

385
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:19,740
Consort Xie, what are you doing?

386
00:18:19,740 --> 00:18:20,540
Please get up.

387
00:18:21,270 --> 00:18:21,730
This...

388
00:18:23,790 --> 00:18:24,720
Physician Xiao,

389
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:28,480
this child

390
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,860
cannot be kept.

391
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:35,750
Why?

392
00:18:37,180 --> 00:18:39,440
Even if the Empress Dowager dislikes it,

393
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:41,080
you still have His Majesty.

394
00:18:41,550 --> 00:18:43,750
It's precisely because of His Majesty,

395
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,750
I cannot be pregnant

396
00:18:50,310 --> 00:18:51,480
if I want to survive.

397
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:54,680
I dare to beg you,

398
00:18:57,590 --> 00:18:59,390
Physician Xiao, please save me.

399
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:12,960
What?

400
00:19:13,510 --> 00:19:14,480
She vomited?

401
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:15,440
Yes.

402
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:17,680
The whole palace is talking about it.

403
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:19,070
Have they found the cause of her vomiting?

404
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:20,720
There are all kinds of rumors.

405
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:21,680
I'm just worried

406
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:22,920
that Dan's food

407
00:19:23,030 --> 00:19:24,490
might have been poisoned.

408
00:19:26,810 --> 00:19:27,810
Damn.

409
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,800
Then this bowl of mine...

410
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,370
Forget what I said.

411
00:19:43,310 --> 00:19:43,770
CEO Dan.

412
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:44,620
CEO Dan.

413
00:19:44,830 --> 00:19:45,510
Come.

414
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:46,760
Come here.

415
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:51,130
Xie Yong'er vomited.

416
00:19:51,770 --> 00:19:53,830
Do you know what that means in a drama?

417
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:54,590
What?

418
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,170
She's pregnant.

419
00:19:56,310 --> 00:19:57,240
She's pregnant?

420
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:58,400
She...

421
00:20:03,830 --> 00:20:05,170
Heaven knows,

422
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,490
I never touched her!

423
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:08,510
I've been sleeping on the floor
in the study for 2 months.

424
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:09,880
My whole body hurts!

425
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:12,710
Why are you laughing?

426
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,550
Someone knows perfectly well

427
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:16,150
whether I touched her or not.

428
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:26,410
I was wondering

429
00:20:26,780 --> 00:20:28,780
why recently every time she sees me,

430
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:31,960
she pounces on me like a hungry tiger.

431
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:35,780
It turns out she wants to find a father

432
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:37,320
for her child.

433
00:20:40,310 --> 00:20:40,970
Be careful.

434
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:46,160
If you hadn't reminded me,
I would have forgotten.

435
00:20:46,160 --> 00:20:47,420
In the original story,

436
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:49,480
Xie Yong'er bravely became pregnant

437
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:51,310
despite pressure from the Empress Dowager

438
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:52,710
and all the other powers.

439
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,650
By the way,

440
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:56,400
the child wasn't yours.

441
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:02,790
This Xiahou Bo...

442
00:21:04,110 --> 00:21:05,170
I didn't expect him

443
00:21:06,350 --> 00:21:07,640
to be so...

444
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:09,380
-bold.
-Reckless!

445
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:12,800
-I really overestimated him!
-I really underestimated him!

446
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:18,030
After all, in the original story,

447
00:21:18,030 --> 00:21:20,490
you, the Emperor,
were surrounded by women.

448
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,350
Even if someone accidentally
became pregnant,

449
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:23,550
she could cover it up.

450
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,750
But our CEO Dan

451
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:29,140
always keeps himself pure

452
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:31,540
and never lets anyone

453
00:21:31,540 --> 00:21:32,310
touch him.

454
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,510
I don't like her.

455
00:21:37,310 --> 00:21:38,710
I never misjudge people.

456
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:41,060
You are the true gentleman,

457
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,400
a breath of fresh air

458
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:45,170
in this bloodthirsty palace.

459
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:50,420
Whether I'm a gentleman or not

460
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,330
depends on who I am with.

461
00:22:03,380 --> 00:22:03,980
Want some?

462
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:09,210
Your Highness,

463
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:11,880
earlier you ordered us to block the envoys
from entering the city.

464
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:14,010
Why are you changing your position now

465
00:22:14,110 --> 00:22:15,550
and supporting the Emperor?

466
00:22:15,550 --> 00:22:16,200
Yes.

467
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:18,980
Didn't you say that if the talks succeed,

468
00:22:19,070 --> 00:22:20,270
the border would be secure

469
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:22,960
and the Empress Dowager would use
the opportunity to reclaim military power

470
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:24,550
and weaken our side?

471
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:26,880
Your Highness, please reconsider.

472
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,480
The ancients said,

473
00:22:31,030 --> 00:22:32,550
"Plan before you act,

474
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:34,580
and know when to stop to gain."

475
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:37,750
But they also said,

476
00:22:39,070 --> 00:22:40,160
"A gentleman acts

477
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:42,770
according to the situation."

478
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:45,400
The Emperor of Yan came under
the pretext of birthday celebration,

479
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:47,270
with the intention of negotiating.

480
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:49,750
People only know the Emperor of Yan
to be weak,

481
00:22:49,750 --> 00:22:51,000
trying to survive

482
00:22:51,790 --> 00:22:53,270
through peace talks.

483
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:54,920
They don't know

484
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:58,700
that while the mantis stalks the cicada,

485
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,960
the oriole is waiting behind.

486
00:23:06,790 --> 00:23:09,450
His Majesty
recently received a secret letter.

487
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:11,830
Emperor of Yan is hospitable.

488
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:13,830
I couldn't refuse his hospitality.

489
00:23:13,960 --> 00:23:15,550
I'm afraid I'll have to stay here
for a few days

490
00:23:15,550 --> 00:23:17,000
and will be late.

491
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:18,590
Wang Zhao.

492
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:20,550
This letter

493
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:22,670
was written by Concubine Yu.

494
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:26,290
So who is this Wang Zhao?

495
00:23:27,110 --> 00:23:27,960
Wang Zhao

496
00:23:29,270 --> 00:23:32,400
is the secret envoy sent by His Majesty.

497
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:33,870
Could it be

498
00:23:34,970 --> 00:23:36,430
that these people from Yan

499
00:23:36,590 --> 00:23:38,190
were invited by the Emperor?

500
00:23:38,590 --> 00:23:40,270
You're very clever, Mr. Cao.

501
00:23:42,310 --> 00:23:44,070
Our puppet Emperor

502
00:23:44,330 --> 00:23:46,250
has finally started to resist,

503
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:49,510
wanting to challenge the Empress Dowager.

504
00:23:49,550 --> 00:23:51,720
Based on
just one letter from Concubine Yu,

505
00:23:51,720 --> 00:23:53,450
are you going to believe it all?

506
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:54,520
Of course not.

507
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:55,770
Huixiao.

508
00:23:56,350 --> 00:23:56,930
I'm here.

509
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:58,740
Tell everyone

510
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:01,110
about what you discovered

511
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:02,110
outside the city.

512
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:02,850
Yes.

513
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,780
I spied on the envoy delegation 30 li

514
00:24:05,780 --> 00:24:06,980
from the city at night

515
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:10,240
and recognized
2 familiar faces in their group.

516
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:12,300
They were Prince Tu'er's trusted men

517
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,540
during the war with Yan State.

518
00:24:15,030 --> 00:24:15,960
That's strange.

519
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:19,440
Tu'er has always been
at odds with the Emperor of Yan.

520
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,980
Why would he send his men for peace talks?

521
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:24,920
So this envoy delegation

522
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:31,200
is a fake.

523
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:42,220
[Capital of Xia]

524
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:54,640
As the saying goes,
don't strike someone with a smiling face.

525
00:24:54,640 --> 00:24:56,580
They've traveled so far.

526
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:58,640
Whether peace talks are possible or not,

527
00:24:58,640 --> 00:25:01,220
turning them away rudely at our gates

528
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:04,480
is not how Great Xia treats guests.

529
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,280
That's right.

530
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:06,830
If word gets out,

531
00:25:07,920 --> 00:25:09,630
it would be embarrassing.

532
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:12,200
Yesterday you said
this would disappoint the soldiers.

533
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:14,590
Why today do you say
it will encourage them?

534
00:25:14,590 --> 00:25:17,000
No principles.
You are unfit to be a minister.

535
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:17,800
Your Majesty,

536
00:25:18,070 --> 00:25:20,640
the Yan people are cunning and
treacherous. We must be cautious.

537
00:25:20,640 --> 00:25:23,170
At most,
we can let them camp outside the city.

538
00:25:23,270 --> 00:25:24,720
They came to congratulate His Majesty

539
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:26,540
on his birthday,

540
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:28,700
yet you make malicious assumptions.

541
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:31,940
Your Majesty,
you must not listen to such slander!

542
00:25:32,110 --> 00:25:32,680
I

543
00:25:33,030 --> 00:25:34,890
am willing to die for my position!

544
00:25:34,920 --> 00:25:37,050
I too am willing to die for my position!

545
00:25:37,160 --> 00:25:39,290
I too am willing to die for my position!

546
00:25:39,550 --> 00:25:41,350
As if you're the only ones willing to die
for your position.

547
00:25:41,350 --> 00:25:41,720
I

548
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:44,570
am also willing to die for my position!

549
00:25:44,590 --> 00:25:47,310
I too am willing to die for my position!

550
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:49,650
What are you doing?

551
00:25:56,270 --> 00:25:59,160
All the civil and military officials
made valid points.

552
00:25:59,160 --> 00:25:59,680
I

553
00:26:01,550 --> 00:26:03,150
find it difficult to decide.

554
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,770
Brother, what do you think?

555
00:26:10,510 --> 00:26:15,430
[Peace and Prosperity]

556
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:13,720
The Yan State sent envoys to negotiate.

557
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,310
At this auspicious moment,

558
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:17,650
we should end the suffering of war

559
00:26:18,070 --> 00:26:19,750
and celebrate peace.

560
00:26:20,500 --> 00:26:22,590
Let it be done!

561
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:24,650
[Peace and Prosperity]

562
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:28,270
They say the Yan people
have 3 heads and 6 arms,

563
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:30,200
but they seem quite ordinary to me.

564
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,870
They do look different from us.

565
00:26:31,870 --> 00:26:33,130
Their eyes are sunken.

566
00:26:33,350 --> 00:26:34,640
Those are the envoys from Yan State?

567
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:35,640
They are so strong.

568
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:36,170
Make way!

569
00:26:36,640 --> 00:26:37,200
Everyone, make way!

570
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:37,920
Make way!

571
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:38,640
I told you so.

572
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,160
Move aside!

573
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:41,290
They really do look different from us.

574
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:42,640
Look at their beards.

575
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:44,360
I heard it was Prince Duan

576
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:46,960
who suggested His Majesty
welcome the delegation into the city.

577
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:48,090
You're all useless!

578
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:51,840
With so many of you,
you couldn't stop one delegation

579
00:26:52,390 --> 00:26:55,400
and actually let them
march into the palace with impunity?

580
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:56,730
And now I'm expected

581
00:26:56,830 --> 00:26:59,830
to dress up and entertain them
with food and drink!

582
00:27:00,370 --> 00:27:01,920
Empress Dowager, please calm your anger!

583
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:03,590
Prince Duan suddenly changed his attitude.

584
00:27:03,590 --> 00:27:04,070
We...

585
00:27:04,920 --> 00:27:06,670
We didn't expect that.

586
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,200
And this time, His Majesty

587
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:11,800
abandoned his usual habit
of procrastination

588
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:13,830
and approved it right in court.

589
00:27:14,830 --> 00:27:15,630
Your Majesty,

590
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:18,440
the guards at the city gate

591
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:20,330
are Prince Duan's men.

592
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:22,600
Almost simultaneously,

593
00:27:22,860 --> 00:27:23,720
the gate opened

594
00:27:24,000 --> 00:27:26,110
and the envoy delegation was welcomed in.

595
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:28,350
If you say His Majesty and Prince Duan
didn't plan this together,

596
00:27:28,350 --> 00:27:29,810
I simply don't believe it.

597
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:36,070
You mean...

598
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:38,860
Prince Duan

599
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:41,200
has joined forces with the Emperor?

600
00:27:46,980 --> 00:27:47,710
Impossible.

601
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:51,240
That's absolutely impossible.

602
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:53,240
Impossible!

603
00:27:54,350 --> 00:27:56,150
Their resentment runs too deep.

604
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:59,830
It has reached the point of life or death.

605
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,310
Your Majesty,

606
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:02,960
I believe

607
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:06,050
instead of blindly guessing their motives,

608
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:08,500
it's better to nip the outcome in the bud.

609
00:28:08,510 --> 00:28:11,240
As the saying goes,
it's better to remove the fire

610
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:14,000
from under the pot
than just to pour water on it.

611
00:28:16,770 --> 00:28:17,900
Mr. Mu is right.

612
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:20,640
These two little brats

613
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:25,360
are using all their tricks
to play games with me.

614
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:29,070
They want peace talks, don't they?

615
00:28:30,110 --> 00:28:30,840
Fine.

616
00:28:31,310 --> 00:28:34,950
I'll make the peace talks
end in complete disaster!

617
00:28:43,590 --> 00:28:44,450
Your Highness,

618
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:46,550
Consort Xie sent a message,

619
00:28:47,310 --> 00:28:48,440
saying it's urgent.

620
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,900
Consort Yu has just left the Cold Palace,

621
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:58,220
and she's already getting restless.

622
00:28:59,390 --> 00:29:01,710
Women's minds are really troublesome.

623
00:29:02,510 --> 00:29:04,640
The maid who delivered the letter said

624
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,830
it's about the child.

625
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:11,480
The child?

626
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:18,950
Didn't everyone already know about her

627
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:22,340
vomiting in the Empress Dowager's chamber?

628
00:29:23,790 --> 00:29:26,050
This pregnancy can't be hidden anymore.

629
00:29:26,710 --> 00:29:28,720
But it gives us another bargaining chip.

630
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:31,450
Let the Empress Dowager
and Emperor fight it out.

631
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:32,880
What's the rush?

632
00:29:34,460 --> 00:29:36,180
[Bo, The Emperor and I were never
intimate. This child cannot be kept.]

633
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:36,200
The Emperor and I were never intimate.

634
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:37,750
[Please help me find a way
to have an abortion. Yong'er]

635
00:29:36,720 --> 00:29:38,180
This child cannot be kept.

636
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,510
Please help me find a way
to have an abortion.

637
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:41,510
This Xie Yong'er!

638
00:29:43,150 --> 00:29:45,150
She kept something this big from me!

639
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,570
Your Highness, it's me.

640
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:49,630
What is it?

641
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,380
Has the letter to His Highness

642
00:29:57,790 --> 00:29:58,590
been sent?

643
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:00,010
Yes, it has.

644
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:01,400
Physician Xiao is here.

645
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,840
Greetings, Consort Xie.

646
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,590
Physician Xiao,

647
00:30:14,350 --> 00:30:16,610
didn't you already refuse me yesterday?

648
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:18,440
Are you here today

649
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,640
just to mock me?

650
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,650
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

651
00:30:25,030 --> 00:30:28,790
Every step in the Imperial Medical Bureau,
from writing the prescription,

652
00:30:28,790 --> 00:30:31,640
preparing the medicine, to decocting it,
is carefully recorded.

653
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:33,770
Each stage is monitored and reviewed.

654
00:30:34,310 --> 00:30:37,440
Abortion medicine
is extremely sensitive in the harem.

655
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,570
Even if I wanted to help,

656
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:42,370
I simply couldn't.

657
00:30:46,590 --> 00:30:49,520
Physician Xiao,
you made yourself clear yesterday.

658
00:30:49,590 --> 00:30:50,830
Why bother

659
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:54,120
repeating yourself?

660
00:30:54,790 --> 00:30:57,450
Do you truly not want this child,
Your Highness?

661
00:30:59,790 --> 00:31:01,920
What woman doesn't long to be a mother,

662
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:05,460
to safely deliver
and raise a healthy child?

663
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:10,690
But as someone in the harem...

664
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,880
I can't even control my own fate,

665
00:31:18,590 --> 00:31:19,920
let alone a child's.

666
00:31:33,110 --> 00:31:34,570
If he comes into this world

667
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:37,930
without being blessed,

668
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,640
only to become

669
00:31:45,070 --> 00:31:47,000
a tool in others' power struggles,

670
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:48,790
to be used,

671
00:31:50,030 --> 00:31:52,510
bullied, oppressed, and persecuted,

672
00:31:55,830 --> 00:31:56,680
I would rather

673
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:02,920
he never existed at all.

674
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:10,520
Since you have made up your mind,

675
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:13,200
I...

676
00:32:14,590 --> 00:32:15,480
will do my best.

677
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:30,830
I've prepared two prescriptions overnight.

678
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:32,470
One for calming nerves and aiding sleep,

679
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:34,470
and one for improving circulation.

680
00:32:34,790 --> 00:32:36,200
Looking at each prescription individually,

681
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:37,860
there's nothing suspicious.

682
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:38,750
And they're both suitable for

683
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:41,410
the condition
I diagnosed you with previously.

684
00:32:41,670 --> 00:32:43,270
However, if taken together,

685
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:45,000
their effects will conflict

686
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:47,600
and become quite similar
to an abortifacient.

687
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:52,440
It's just that...

688
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:00,470
What?

689
00:33:01,270 --> 00:33:02,520
I feel guilty.

690
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:06,350
Although I've repeatedly
adjusted this medicine

691
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:08,200
to make it as gentle as possible,

692
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:10,770
it's still not a conventional method.

693
00:33:11,720 --> 00:33:13,120
It's impossible to avoid

694
00:33:13,390 --> 00:33:15,720
the physical harm caused by miscarriage.

695
00:33:18,360 --> 00:33:19,220
That's enough.

696
00:33:23,420 --> 00:33:25,270
Physician Xiao,
you're risking yourself to help me.

697
00:33:25,270 --> 00:33:26,270
I'll never forget

698
00:33:26,550 --> 00:33:27,750
your great kindness.

699
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:29,250
I only hope that one day,

700
00:33:29,730 --> 00:33:30,200
I

701
00:33:32,040 --> 00:33:33,500
might be of service to you.

702
00:33:36,570 --> 00:33:38,900
Your Highness, you don't need to say that.

703
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:41,540
Your Highness, please rise.

704
00:33:50,810 --> 00:33:53,030
This medicine
must be taken for 3 consecutive days

705
00:33:53,030 --> 00:33:53,890
to take effect.

706
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:57,510
During this time,
you must not drink alcohol

707
00:33:57,510 --> 00:33:59,110
or take any other medicines.

708
00:33:59,580 --> 00:34:01,070
When walking or lying down,

709
00:34:01,070 --> 00:34:02,870
you must move gently and slowly.

710
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:13,860
Please follow these instructions
carefully, Your Highness.

711
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:20,090
It needs three days?

712
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:23,659
Can it work any faster?

713
00:34:23,659 --> 00:34:26,440
Medicines that work immediately
are extremely dangerous.

714
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,300
Your Highness,

715
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,980
you mustn't try them.

716
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,760
Zhang San's Diary.

717
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:15,710
Dan,

718
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,700
you haven't been to

719
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:20,880
the Imperial Study for half a month.

720
00:35:20,890 --> 00:35:23,960
The whole palace is buzzing with gossip,

721
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:27,190
saying you not only dislike studying,

722
00:35:27,710 --> 00:35:29,330
but also try every means

723
00:35:29,550 --> 00:35:31,280
to humiliate your classmates.

724
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,930
What's the reason for this?

725
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:35,730
If this continues,

726
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:39,000
even I won't be able
to back you up anymore.

727
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,820
Who was really humiliating them?

728
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:46,670
You should know that better than I do.

729
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:48,810
Then tell me,

730
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:50,990
and I'll stand up for you.

731
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:56,190
Who else could it be?

732
00:36:00,150 --> 00:36:02,460
I treat you like my own child!

733
00:36:00,390 --> 00:36:01,630
[To Father]

734
00:36:05,190 --> 00:36:06,240
Who wrote this?

735
00:36:07,190 --> 00:36:08,620
Did you write this?

736
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:11,150
How dare you write a letter secretly

737
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:14,080
to your father
with false accusations against me!

738
00:36:14,550 --> 00:36:17,280
You disappointed me completely.

739
00:36:19,030 --> 00:36:20,670
Has all my love and care for you

740
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:22,470
all these years

741
00:36:23,070 --> 00:36:23,840
been

742
00:36:25,590 --> 00:36:26,840
for nothing?

743
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:30,240
Father is the Emperor!

744
00:36:36,670 --> 00:36:37,510
The Emperor?

745
00:36:40,590 --> 00:36:41,990
He's the Emperor, right?

746
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:48,690
Go and ask.

747
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,700
In our court and harem,

748
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,750
which Emperor

749
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:54,960
has ever really been in charge?

750
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:55,920
Child,

751
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,110
wake up.

752
00:37:00,480 --> 00:37:01,480
I

753
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,590
won't hide it from you.

754
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:09,110
In my entire life,

755
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:11,490
I've hated many people.

756
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:14,320
The one I hate most

757
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:17,400
is your father.

758
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:20,560
But...

759
00:37:22,070 --> 00:37:23,410
he's about to die.

760
00:37:26,110 --> 00:37:26,510
You...

761
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,600
What did you do to him?

762
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:35,840
Look.

763
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,350
This little face.

764
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:40,540
When you're angry,

765
00:37:41,230 --> 00:37:43,400
you look just like your father.

766
00:37:45,590 --> 00:37:46,290
Dan,

767
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:49,150
listen to me.

768
00:37:50,590 --> 00:37:51,640
If you

769
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:55,590
don't want to stand with me,

770
00:37:56,670 --> 00:37:58,340
there are other princes.

771
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:02,190
No.

772
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:05,380
I mean other crown princes!

773
00:38:13,710 --> 00:38:14,210
Mother!

774
00:38:15,670 --> 00:38:16,270
Mother!

775
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,240
I was wrong!

776
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,130
I've been unfilial!

777
00:38:21,320 --> 00:38:23,800
I've failed your kindness.

778
00:38:24,590 --> 00:38:25,660
I beg you for mercy

779
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:27,880
and spare my life!

780
00:38:32,110 --> 00:38:33,420
Alright.

781
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:35,400
If you know you're wrong,

782
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:37,280
just don't do it again.

783
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:39,320
But Dan,

784
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,510
let me remind you,

785
00:38:42,190 --> 00:38:43,630
don't try

786
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,860
to go against me.

787
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:49,110
You haven't even seen

788
00:38:50,030 --> 00:38:51,630
the love I have for you yet.
